block content

	section#about.section.align-center
		.container
			.icon.section-icon.icon-multimedia-12
			h3 You want to be at #LRTF 2018
			p.text-alt This will be a full two days of  format, hosted on October 4th and 5th<br class="hidden-sm hidden-xs"/> at the Statehouse Convention Center in Little Rock, Arkansas.

			.col-sm-6
				p.align-left Little Rock Tech Fest is an annual developer conference featuring popular web, mobile, database, devops and related developer topics from industry leaders. It is the event in Little Rock for both professional and aspiring software developers. Speakers from across the country come to present. Students and professionals from across Arkansas and surrounding regions come to learn and network with peers.


			.col-sm-6
				p.align-left Our purpose is to encourage local professionals to increase their skills and to promote the Little Rock region to both experienced and aspiring developers and students.

				p.align-left This is our fifth year hosting the event.  Will you join us?

	section#location
		.contacts-wrapper
			#contacts-map.map(data-settings="/data/map-settings.json" style="height:560px;")

			.container.contacts-on-map-container
				.contacts-on-map
					h3 Event Location
					h5 Statehouse Convention Center
					ul.list
						li
							i.fa.fa-map-marker
							span 101 E Markham St, Little Rock, AR 72201
						li
							i.fa.fa-map-o
							a(href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Statehouse+Convention+Center/@34.7487084,-92.2728966,17z/data=!4m13!1m7!3m6!1s0x87d2bb7c7d42bb63:0x1700cdf88779977b!2sStatehouse+Convention+Center!3b1!8m2!3d34.7487084!4d-92.2707079!3m4!1s0x87d2bb7c7d42bb63:0x1700cdf88779977b!8m2!3d34.7487084!4d-92.2707079" target="_blank") Get directions


